%% Diagram: Diagram 1
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TD
    A[Need bundle splitting] --> B{Multiple teams or independent deploys?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Module Federation]
    B -->|No| D{App type}
    D -->|SPA| E[Route-based splitting]
    D -->|MPA| F[Entry point splitting]
    E --> G{Heavy components on some routes?}
    G -->|Yes| H[Add component splitting]
    G -->|No| I[Route splitting only]
    F --> J{Large shared deps?}
    J -->|Yes| K[Add vendor splitting]
    J -->|No| L[Entry splitting only]
    H --> K
    I --> K
